{"tid":95063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真的要築牆了! Trump將在明日簽行政命令","createTime":"2017-01-25T17:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T08:27:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14a4b13bf24629fdd99083c566b030ba1d8f7aa8","tid":95063,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>真的要築牆了！川普將在明日簽行政命令</strong><br />\n2017-01-25  12:30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php81nr09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php81nr09.jpg&h=294fae7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n川普將在明日簽署一系列打擊非法移民的行政命令。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普最受矚目的政策之一，就是要在美墨邊境築牆，防止非法移民進入美國。如今這項承諾有望兌現，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為川普將在明日簽署行政命令，下令築牆。</span><br />\n<br />\n川普在推特上宣佈，「明天是美國國家安全計畫的大日子，我們將要築牆！」除了在美墨邊境築牆外，川普也將對敘利亞及其他難民下逐客令，並限制對伊拉克、伊朗、利比亞、索馬利亞、蘇丹、葉門等國發出簽證。<br />\n<br />\n川普上任至今效率驚人，已分別簽署了包括準備廢除歐巴馬健保、退出TPP、恢復輸油管計畫等行政命令，預計在明天落實他的非法移民政策，且這一天同時是墨西哥外交部長抵達華盛頓，為墨國總統與川普在月底會面做行前準備的日子。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1958240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1958240&d=pWRanps2weUGMQ9AXhniRGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=eb309a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1958240&h=0e5d78f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1958240</a>"},{"pid":"5ff9053926605379afb4700740f3ba3ca68764b5","tid":95063,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"封埋啲地道先講啦"},{"pid":"2d088dcb39b5c85e1380c3eaf9310231d6d2bd9f","tid":95063,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>封埋啲地道先講啦</blockquote><br />\n咩地道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset